reviewText: Excellent!  I know there are all types of nurses but there is the core that remains the same for all nurses and it was shown here.  Very well done!  Bravo!

As a nurse nothing inspires me more than the stories of other nurses. Beautifully captured, realistic representation of the things we do and people we are. If you know ANYONE thinking of going to school for nursing or nursing assistant this would be a great piece for them to watch.
Great documentary giving an insight into the heart of nursing. There is a multiude of speciality areas for nurses to share their caring hearts. What an awesome tribute to a selfless profession!
Very moving, This truly speaks volumes of the deep personalized caring, compassion and love nurses show their patients.
Amazing, inspirational story of how nurses help patients through birth and death and older age.
Where can I buy this DVD???..I need to show this to fledglings!
Wonderfu! Finally a true Nurse Story.
